Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.59,0:01:48.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海贼…载着黑色野望的船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.45,0:02:10.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终於又要出战了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.08,0:02:14.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有这么庞大的军队，谁都不用怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.79,0:02:16.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡修王万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.40,0:02:34.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么…那个亚喜拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.18,0:02:46.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了想得到战之守护神麻利教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.35,0:02:49.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最高司祭欧布的帮助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.22,0:02:51.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到神殿的卡修和帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.26,0:02:53.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道欧布与亚喜拉在一起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.79,0:02:56.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到亚喜拉早来一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.46,0:02:58.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这都怪我不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.10,0:03:04.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡修殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.54,0:03:12.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意，帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.88,0:03:16.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是多个要打败的敌人而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.68,0:03:20.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老实讲我也不想让他变成敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.65,0:03:22.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.46,0:03:26.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在最重要就是打败煞星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.00,0:03:31.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.37,0:03:34.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希利斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.83,0:03:37.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜帕母，又要分开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.20,0:03:38.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.41,0:03:41.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希利斯，你们不是也要走了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.41,0:03:43.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用整顿一下吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.84,0:03:46.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道，很喜欢生气的人   再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.78,0:03:52.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，蒂都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.45,0:03:55.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很紧张的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.96,0:03:59.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，因为我是森林精灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.93,0:04:01.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以对沙漠不习惯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.86,0:04:05.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你经过那么多次沙漠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.43,0:04:07.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起，蒂都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.97,0:04:09.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.72,0:04:25.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终於走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.22,0:04:28.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在帕母他们将煞星魔龙打败时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.42,0:04:31.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望我们把事情也办好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.29,0:04:33.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.33,0:04:36.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们也要开始准备了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.93,0:04:39.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长请下命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.37,0:04:47.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出发   往自由都市莱登去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.49,0:05:04.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来，不要过来，救命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.43,0:05:15.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丰收，丰收，想不到这么简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.77,0:05:18.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快搬，快点搬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.28,0:05:26.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次从麻莫来这里就没白费了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.28,0:05:31.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，最初我以为不适合我做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.22,0:05:34.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有等亚喜拉来这种工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.02,0:05:38.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是份好工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.36,0:05:42.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚鲁亥布，亚喜拉大人到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.66,0:05:46.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚…亚喜拉大人他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.94,0:05:56.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等你好久了，亚喜拉大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.54,0:05:57.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没发生意外就放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.35,0:06:04.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讲没发生意外!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.45,0:06:11.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可没叫你们在这里当海盗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.89,0:06:15.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是我们是艄战船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.46,0:06:19.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然抢来的财宝也有想分一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.77,0:06:21.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给麻莫王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.77,0:06:23.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了，快去准备船吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.17,0:06:26.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我最初给你们的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.87,0:06:28.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.24,0:06:31.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了就往青龙岛出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.04,0:06:34.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想去见水龙，快去办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.32,0:06:37.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在去办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.89,0:06:42.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目标就只有一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.46,0:06:44.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是支配的王锡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.62,0:06:48.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果水龙身上没有我们就回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.53,0:06:50.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果它身上有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.56,0:06:54.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就一定要和它战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.57,0:06:56.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那水龙只要还受古代魔法王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.94,0:07:01.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔法指令，它就一定要保住它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.28,0:07:09.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能做的就尽量去做，对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.15,0:07:14.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙并不是不可以讲和的动物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.95,0:07:18.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们最先要做的就是确定宝物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.62,0:07:22.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个计画好像交给你比较安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.00,0:07:24.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上，亚喜拉大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.43,0:07:27.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.50,0:07:30.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有，因为我是魔术师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.37,0:07:33.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到这个地方让我觉得很好奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.81,0:07:36.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以想四处看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.44,0:07:41.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗，小心别掉到悬崖下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.88,0:07:44.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有，帮我和巴格那问好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚喜拉今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.60,0:08:03.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,往有水龙的青龙岛去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.07,0:08:07.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定会拿到东西的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.57,0:08:10.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但亚喜拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.24,0:08:14.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像知道巴大人的计画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.88,0:08:18.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果没那种机心的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.42,0:08:19.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我来讲，就是个普通人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.42,0:08:23.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿灵魂的水晶球时也是一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.06,0:08:27.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次的报告希望在得到宝物後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.16,0:08:28.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.57,0:08:36.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,复兴卡狄斯国的日子要接近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.17,0:08:39.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到那时候我就可以排除万难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.44,0:08:42.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成为至高的主宰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.92,0:08:57.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫古娄达的人不可以相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.22,0:09:01.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他好像有什么隐瞒着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.33,0:09:05.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道，不只有他一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.93,0:09:08.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡贝拉和亚斯达鲁也是一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.50,0:09:11.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,士兵司梅和奇努拉以外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.34,0:09:17.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他三人都是麻莫下的大臣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.08,0:09:20.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那这样就要更加小心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.61,0:09:22.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样的小事就怕的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.75,0:09:24.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就不配在麻莫下做事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.08,0:09:27.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.69,0:09:30.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讲的对，不惧怕那些恶魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.46,0:09:32.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是做勇者的条件之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.23,0:09:36.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，然後新勇者一定会得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.10,0:09:38.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己想得到的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.11,0:09:53.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.31,0:09:55.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到达自由都市莱登了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.72,0:09:59.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是最近因为多次被海盗抢劫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.52,0:10:02.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以都没人借船载他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.42,0:10:04.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去青龙岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.34,0:10:17.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.40,0:10:22.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是，怕海盗还敢以船家为名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.28,0:10:29.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别这样，别人没你那么厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.95,0:10:32.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样，把海盗给打败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.92,0:10:35.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就我们几个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.02,0:10:37.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打海盗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.22,0:10:39.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你要讲什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.43,0:10:42.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道你忘记我们的目标吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.59,0:10:43.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.20,0:10:46.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我讨厌喜欢战争士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.80,0:10:47.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讲什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.03,0:10:49.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样让我帮你们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.14,0:10:52.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.47,0:10:55.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草原的精灵吟游诗人对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.54,0:11:01.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做马卢，我知道不少事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.78,0:11:06.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,例如关於海盗的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.59,0:11:08.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.69,0:11:09.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.82,0:11:12.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是条件是要带我去好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.33,0:11:18.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑，这么好的事谁会信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.50,0:11:20.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么，快放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢西努真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.50,0:11:24.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是帕母的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.17,0:11:26.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定会赞成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.64,0:11:28.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讲得对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.64,0:11:33.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们去打海盗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.42,0:11:47.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在讲什么，你是认真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.46,0:11:51.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很简单的事，只要海盗还在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.60,0:11:53.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船就一定不会出海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.67,0:11:55.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以只有将海盗赶走这个办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.64,0:11:57.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是这样讲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.14,0:12:00.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的情报如果是真的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.67,0:12:04.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们也许会有赢的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.38,0:12:07.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个哥哥真通情达理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.58,0:12:08.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有另一个原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.55,0:12:10.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一个原因!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.32,0:12:12.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要把海盗船抢过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.65,0:12:15.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样我们就有船用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.69,0:12:21.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此，这样决定了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.96,0:12:24.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家应该没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.00,0:12:27.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,选你当队长真的是正确的选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.13,0:12:29.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的和帕母一模一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.30,0:12:32.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然决定了，在战争之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.14,0:12:34.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就要喝个通宵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.64,0:12:37.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么你们就用这个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.48,0:12:41.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是我的钱包吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.45,0:12:43.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小子，你什么时候拿走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.12,0:12:44.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.45,0:12:46.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.79,0:12:48.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.12,0:12:51.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你很在意刚才那句话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.92,0:12:52.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那句话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.53,0:12:55.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是如果帕母的话  一定会答应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.26,0:12:59.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是因为帕母  所以你才答应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.07,0:13:02.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我的理由就是刚讲的那些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.93,0:13:03.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.84,0:13:04.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.90,0:13:07.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你至少要装出嫉妒的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.67,0:13:10.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这样让我好没面子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.95,0:13:18.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯林他们不知道怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.25,0:13:20.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森不知道有没有尽职
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.02,0:13:23.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的，一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.82,0:13:25.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯林选出来的队长，一定不会错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.53,0:13:31.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且波里森如果可以解除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.46,0:13:34.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愤怒精灵的诅咒，被魔女米尔拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.13,0:13:37.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,控制的魂也应该会痊愈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.20,0:13:39.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是斯林所想要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.41,0:13:42.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是斯林也真爱管闲事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.91,0:13:44.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然为了别人那么的费心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.24,0:13:48.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类真有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.35,0:13:51.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做精灵的我很难可以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.19,0:13:57.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒂都，你讲得对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.72,0:14:02.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃饱工作，教小孩读书识字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.26,0:14:05.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实是斯林的愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.23,0:14:11.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…时代并不允许这样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.27,0:14:14.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.74,0:14:18.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想不想建立个王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.78,0:14:24.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在只有一点一点的去实现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.48,0:14:26.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧，蒂都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.79,0:14:34.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.73,0:14:35.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母，你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.93,0:14:37.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是 ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.67,0:14:50.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真残忍，这个村子真可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.38,0:14:55.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也是煞星龙做的吗，真残忍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.12,0:15:01.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猎龙时都会有这种事情发生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.32,0:15:04.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就在这里等它，听到了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.39,0:15:06.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它真的会来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.36,0:15:11.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定会，它好像不喜欢有人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.63,0:15:13.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑进它的领域内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.89,0:15:44.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.40,0:15:49.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还算是男人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.81,0:16:00.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会感冒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.91,0:16:03.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.16,0:16:14.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你至少也装出一点嫉妒的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.53,0:16:18.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系，一定可以帮你找回感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.53,0:16:21.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对你强烈的意识有信心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.64,0:16:29.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那愤怒精灵的真正面目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.48,0:16:38.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐，从这里开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.72,0:16:40.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从这里开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.59,0:16:43.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就被愤怒精灵控制了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.04,0:17:03.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森，对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.68,0:17:07.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愤怒，快愤怒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.11,0:17:10.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐 ... 姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.42,0:17:14.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手，住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.36,0:17:28.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愤怒，然後将全部毁掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.17,0:17:36.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愤怒，然後将全部毁掉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.14,0:17:39.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愤怒，毁掉全部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.01,0:17:41.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森，对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.31,0:17:42.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.84,0:18:06.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差一点就有事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.11,0:18:09.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做这种危险的测验
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.28,0:18:13.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但真的有效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.15,0:18:16.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听得见愤怒精灵的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.96,0:18:31.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.38,0:18:52.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.19,0:19:01.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.63,0:19:03.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煞星魔龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.14,0:19:17.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终於要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.01,0:19:19.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我们的对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.45,0:19:22.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么会那么大